Class DemoUtilities

java.lang.Object
  demoClient.DemoUtilities

public class DemoUtilities
extends java.lang.Object

This class helps to display the bus stations from Toulouse in the map, using the local file "txt/listBusStations.txt" that contains a list of bus stations from Toulouse and their Coordinates.

Version:
1.0 30/01/2014
Author:
Luc Clement, Arnaud Saunier

getCoordinateFromStation

public static org.openstreetmap.gui.jmapviewer.Coordinate getCoordinateFromStation(java.lang.String nameStation)
Returns the Coordinate of a given bus station from Toulouse. Returns null if the name is unknown (in the local file "txt/listBusStations.txt")

Parameters:
nameStation - The name of the stations (without space)
Returns:
the coordinate of the station or null if this stations is not referenced.

drawAllBusStations

Display all the bus stations referenced in the local file "txt/listBusStations.txt" on the DisplayMap given in argument

Parameters:
myDisplayMap - the DisplayMap on which we have to draw all the bus stations.
